sbol:ComponentDefinition.dcterms:title: BBa_M39413
sbol:ComponentDefinition.dcterms:description: flipable pCat promoter regulated by fimE recombinase
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableProvenance: This part is a combination of several other parts from the registry
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableDescription:
pCat promoter ([[BBa_I14033]]) flanked by regions ([[BBa_K137010]], [[BBa_K137008]]) recognized by fimE recombinase ([[BBa_K137007]]).
pCat is a constitutive promoter, which enables this device to be used as a switch to constitutively express two different regions. By default, the upstream sense strand is promoted. When flipped, the downstream antisense strand is promoted.
Additionally, downstream of the promoter is a terminating sequence [[BBa_B0015]]. This sequence is to prevent "backwards" transcription before the promoter is flipped. It is between the recombinant regions, causing it to flip with the promoter.
pCat can be replaced with another promoter for additional regulation if needed.
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableNotes: The double terminator placed before the promoter prevents any transient backwards transcription. Although the amount of transcription would be small, this design allows for stronger "digital" behavior.
sbol:ComponentDefinition.dc:creator: Zach Banks

sbol:ComponentDefinition.dcterms:title: BBa_B0012
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableProvenance: Derived from the TE terminator of T7 bacteriophage between Genes 1.3 and 1.4 <genbank>V01146</genbank>.
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableDescription: Transcription terminator for the E.coli RNA polymerase.
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableNotes:
Suggested by Sri Kosuri and Drew Endy as a high efficiency terminator. The 5' end cutoff was placed immediately after the TAA stop codon and the 3' end cutoff was placed just prior to the RBS of Gene 1.4 (before AAGGAG).

Use anywhere transcription should be stopped when the gene of interest is upstream of this terminator.
sbol:ComponentDefinition.dc:creator: Reshma Shetty

sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableDescription: Transcriptional terminator consisting of a 64 bp stem-loop.
sbol:ComponentDefinition.dc:creator: Randy Rettberg
